{"view":"article","slug":"pyraminx-oka-bell","category":"CHS","subcategory":null,"topDir":"CHS","title":{"zh":"金字塔冈法"},"content":{"zh":"<p><strong>金字塔冈法</strong></p><p><strong>开始</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>在同一个角下，还原一个棱并做一个冈（色向错误且在错误槽的棱）</p><p><strong>底心</strong></p><p>与空穴法的对应步骤类似。</p><p><strong>冈和空穴</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R'\">R U R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U R\">R' U R</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"L R L' U' R'\">L R L' U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R' L' R U L\">R' L' R U L</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(R' U R' U') (R U R)\">(R' U R' U') (R U R)</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>ELL</strong></p><p>与空穴法的对应步骤相同。</p><p><strong>金字塔铃法</strong></p><p><strong>开始</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>在同一个角下，还原一个棱并做一个铃（色向正确且在错误槽的棱）</p><p><strong>底心</strong></p><p>与空穴法的对应步骤类似。</p><p><strong>铃和空穴</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>S</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>H</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2' L R L' R\">R2' L R L' R</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"L2 R' L' R L'\">L2 R' L' R L'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"L R L' U' R'\">L R L' U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R' L' R U L\">R' L' R U L</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"S (R L R' L')\">S (R L R' L')</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>ELL</strong></p><p><a id=\"_Hlk294819\"></a>与空穴法的对应步骤相同。</p>"},"algs":["R U R'","R' U R","L R L' U' R'","R' L' R U L","(R' U R' U') (R U R)","R2' L R L' R","L2 R' L' R L'","S (R L R' L')"],"thumb":"/stats/alg/media/pyraminx-oka-bell/zh/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
